and\" title=\"Skeletal Hand\">Skeletal Hand</a></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Prehistoric Scapula.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ee/Prehistoric_Scapula.png/24px-Prehistoric_Scapula.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ee/Prehistoric_Scapula.png/36px-Prehistoric_Scapula.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/ee/Prehistoric_Scapula.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Prehistoric_Scapula\" title=\"Prehistoric Scapula\">Prehistoric Scapula</a></span>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Sloth Skeleton L.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/6e/Sloth_Skeleton_L.png/36px-Sloth_Skeleton_L.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"36\" height=\"68\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6e/Sloth_Skeleton_L.png 1.5x\" /> <a href=\"/Sloth_Skeleton\" title=\"Sloth Skeleton\">Sloth Skeleton L</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Prehistoric Rib.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/62/Prehistoric_Rib.png/24px-Prehistoric_Rib.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/62/Prehistoric_Rib.png/36px-Prehistoric_Rib.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/62/Prehistoric_Rib.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Prehistoric_Rib\" title=\"Prehistoric Rib\">Prehistoric Rib</a></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Prehistoric Vertebra.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e9/Prehistoric_Vertebra.png/24px-Prehistoric_Vertebra.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e9/Prehistoric_Vertebra.png/36px-Prehistoric_Vertebra.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e9/Prehistoric_Vertebra.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Prehistoric_Vertebra\" title=\"Prehistoric Vertebra\">Prehistoric Vertebra</a></span>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Sloth Skeleton M.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/be/Sloth_Skeleton_M.png/36px-Sloth_Skeleton_M.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"36\" height=\"68\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/b/be/Sloth_Skeleton_M.png 1.5x\" /> <a href=\"/Sloth_Skeleton\" title=\"Sloth Skeleton\">Sloth Skeleton M</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Prehistoric Tibia.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ce/Prehistoric_Tibia.png/24px-Prehistoric_Tibia.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ce/Prehistoric_Tibia.png/36px-Prehistoric_Tibia.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/ce/Prehistoric_Tibia.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Prehistoric_Tibia\" title=\"Prehistoric Tibia\">Prehistoric Tibia</a></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Skeletal Tail.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/29/Skeletal_Tail.png/24px-Skeletal_Tail.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/29/Skeletal_Tail.png/36px-Skeletal_Tail.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/2/29/Skeletal_Tail.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Skeletal_Tail\" title=\"Skeletal Tail\">Skeletal Tail</a></span>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Sloth Skeleton R.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e7/Sloth_Skeleton_R.png/36px-Sloth_Skeleton_R.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"36\" height=\"68\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e7/Sloth_Skeleton_R.png 1.5x\" /> <a href=\"/Sloth_Skeleton\" title=\"Sloth Skeleton\">Sloth Skeleton R</a></span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Books\">Books</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Museum&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Books\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>Main article: <a href=\"/Lost_Books\" title=\"Lost Books\">Lost Books</a></i></dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Achievements\">Achievements</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Museum&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Achievements\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>There are 2 <a href=\"/Achievements\" title=\"Achievements\">Achievements</a> associated with donating <a href=\"/Artifacts\" title=\"Artifacts\">Artifacts</a> or <a href=\"/Minerals\" title=\"Minerals\">Minerals</a> to the Museum.\n</p>\n<ul><li>Treasure Trove (Donate 40 different items to the museum)</li>\n<li>A Complete Collection (Complete the museum collection)</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Museum&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>There is a total of 102 spaces available for donations to be placed but a total of only 95 available items to be donated. Six spaces in the center of the largest table cannot be reached to examine items placed on them, so it may be advisable to leave this area empty.\n<ul><li>If using a controller, any diagonal item may be unreachable for examination once donated.</li></ul></li>\n<li>To move items inside the donation interface on Switch, go to \"Options\" and disable \"Use Controller Style Menus\".</li>\n<li>In iOS (and possibly other mobile versions) items on the bottom most row cannot be moved in the donation interface. However, if the character goes to the front desk one tile to the left of Gunther, they get the option to rearrange the collection (even without completing the collection). In this mode, all the items are moveable.</li></ul>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-packed\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 304.66666666667px\"><div style=\"width: 304.66666666667px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 302.66666666667px;\"><div style=\"margin:0px auto;\"><a href=\"/File:Stardew_Museum_Interior.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/2d/Stardew_Museum_Interior.png/454px-Stardew_Museum_Interior.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"303\" height=\"240\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/2d/Stardew_Museum_Interior.png/682px-Stardew_Museum_Interior.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/2/2d/Stardew_Museum_Interior.png/909px-Stardew_Museum_Interior.png 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>Museum Interior with unreachable tiles shaded\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 305.33333333333px\"><div style=\"width: 305.33333333333px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 303.33333333333px;\"><div style=\"margin:0px auto;\"><a href=\"/File:Stardew_Museum_Organized.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/64/Stardew_Museum_Organized.png/455px-Stardew_Museum_Organized.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"304\" height=\"240\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/64/Stardew_Museum_Organized.png/682px-Stardew_Museum_Organized.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/6/64/Stardew_Museum_Organized.png/910px-Stardew_Museum_Organized.png 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>One example of an organized complete collection\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Museum&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.3.32\" title=\"Version History\">1.3.32</a>: Fixed inability to place donated items on the bottom two rows of the museum.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Added donation rewards for 35, 70, 80, and 90 items donated. Added ability to rearrange the museum artifacts without having to donate a new one. Fixed bug where movement of inventory inside donation screen would prevent donation of items. Fixed issue in multiplayer where rearranging the collection would result in the message that a new item was donated. Various other museum-donation related fixes.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: <a href=\"/Museum#Donation_Rewards\" title=\"Museum\">Museum donation</a> interactions improved.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6.9\" title=\"Version History\">1.6.9</a>: The description of Artifacts and Minerals does not appear on the <a href=\"/Collections\" title=\"Collections\">Collections</a> tab until the items are donated to the Museum.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"3\">Buildings\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Merchants\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Abandoned_House\" title=\"Abandoned House\">Abandoned House</a> • <a href=\"/Adventurer%27s_Guild\" title=\"Adventurer&#39;s Guild\">Adventurer's Guild</a> • <a href=\"/Blacksmith\" title=\"Blacksmith\">Blacksmith</a> • <a href=\"/Bookseller\" title=\"Bookseller\">Bookseller</a> • <a href=\"/Carpenter%27s_Shop\" title=\"Carpenter&#39;s Shop\">Carpenter's Shop</a> • <a href=\"/Casino\" title=\"Casino\">Casino</a> • <a href=\"/Desert_Trader\" title=\"Desert Trader\">Desert Trader</a> • <a href=\"/Fish_Shop\" title=\"Fish Shop\">Fish Shop</a> • <a href=\"/Giant_Stump\